@startuml
title Write a Review - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Pet Owner" as Owner
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "reviews-service\nReviewController" as Reviews
participant "ReviewService" as Service
participant "RemoteClientsFacade" as Remote
participant "visits-service" as Visits
participant "ContentModerator" as Moderator
database "reviews schema" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ

Owner -> Web: Submit rating and text
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/reviews
Gateway -> Reviews: route with USER JWT
Reviews -> Service: createReview(request, author)
Service -> Remote: verify eligibility
Remote -> Visits: check completed visit / target relation
Visits --> Remote: eligible
Service -> Moderator: scan profanity / policy
alt clean text
  Service -> DB: save PUBLISHED or PENDING_MODERATION
  Service -> MQ: publish ReviewCreatedEvent
  Reviews --> Web: ReviewResponse
else not eligible or blocked
  Service --> Reviews: ProblemDetail
  Reviews --> Web: error
end
@enduml
